Class ChunkedRecordStream

    public class ChunkedRecordStream
extends AbstractStream<java.util.List<Record>>
implements NextUntilNull<java.util.List<Record>>
    A chunked record stream groups subsequent records that share the value for one field, the key. All consecutive records that have the same value in the key column are accumulated in a List, one list for each value.
